msgstr "<phrase>Algteguriteks lahutamise ülesanne</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter a factor by clicking on the prime factor buttons. The "
"<quote>x</quote> sign is automatically inserted, when you click the next "
"prime factor button. You can remove the last entered prime factor by "
"clicking on the <guibutton>Backspace</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Algteguri saab sisestada klõpsuga algteguri nuppudel. Märk <quote>x</quote> "
"lisatakse automaatselt, kui klõpsad järgmisel algteguri nupul Viimase "
"sisestatud algteguri saab eemaldada klõpsuga nupule <guimenu>Backspace</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have entered all prime factors click on the <guibutton>Check</"
"guibutton> button. &kbruch; will check your input and present the correct "
"result. After this step you will get to the next task by clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled enda arvates kõik algtegurid kirja pannud, klõpsa nupule "
"<guimenu>Kontrolli</guimenu>. &kbruch; uurib siis sinu arvamust ja näitab "
"õiget vastust. Pärast seda võid asuda uue ülesande kallale, klõpsates nupule "
"<guimenu>Edasi</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the screenshot at the top of this page you can see a <quote>x</quote> "
"between the prime factors. This is the multiplication sign. The product of "
"all prime factors must be the number you try to factorize."
msgstr ""
"Lehekülje ülaosas asuval pildil on algtegurite vahel näha märk <quote>x</"
"quote>. See on korrutusmärk. Kõigi algtegurite korrutis ongi see number, "
"mida sul tuleb lahutada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You have to enter all prime factors even when a prime factor repeats several "
"times. Example: As prime factors of number 18 you have to enter 2, 3 and 3."
msgstr ""
"Sisestada tuleb kõik algtegurid - ka siis, kui mõni algtegur peaks esinema "
"mitu korda. Näide: 18 algteguritena tuleb sisestada 2, 3 ja 3."

